{=% endfor =%}

Useful capability-source surfaces include:
{=% for capability_source_type in capability_source_types =%}
- `{= capability_source_type =}`
{=% endfor =%}

Useful independent corroboration source types include:
{=% for corroboration_source_type in corroboration_source_types =%}
